= Research Details

I am currently working in the area of Network Design & Dimensioning, traffic measurements and WAN optimization. During my PhD, I had the pleasure to work with IBM, and on several projects funded by Cisco, Time Warner Cable and ITng Institute. 

Moreover, I had the pleasure to visit and present my work in IBM TJ Watson Research Center NY USA, Edge Router Business Unit of Cisco in Ottawa Canada, and VTT Technical Research Center of Finland.

My undergraduate thesis was based on Analysis and Simulation of the QoS in WLANs.

